    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The engine and transmission are solid with no major leaks, though the high mileage is evident in the car's overall feel. Cosmetically, the exterior has several noticeable scratches, small door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and staining, and some of the plastic trim pieces are loose or cracked. While it won't win any beauty contests, it has been regularly maintained and is ready for the road.",
