    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional mechanical integrity and refined aesthetic appeal. This unit has been meticulously curated to ensure reliable performance and long-term value. With a well-documented service history and a clean profile, it represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver who prioritizes quality and consistency. Experience the perfect balance of sophistication and durability.",
      "price": 36800.0,
