    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs super smoothly and has been well-taken care of over the years. It's perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that's ready for many more adventures. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it feels on the road!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
