    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure timing remains precise. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile shifts to the rear wheels through a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein B16 coilovers, optimizing corner-exit traction and roll center. While the exterior displays a light patina expected of a driven enthusiast car, the engine's compression figures are strong and the rod bearings have been addressed. This is a driver-spec machine engineered for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
