    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been a dependable and well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior maintains a strong curb appeal with a deep finish, showing only minor stone chips and light surface marks typical of regular use. Inside, the interior is clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is intact, and all power features, including the infotainment and climate control, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from regular synthetic oil changes. It has recently passed a full safety inspection and comes with a documented service history. This is a solid, honest example of a vehicle that is ready for many more miles of trouble-free driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a premier balance of performance and value. This unit has undergone a rigorous professional inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic standards that exceed market expectations. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, this vehicle represents an ideal acquisition for those who demand reliability without compromising on executive presence. Experience the assurance of quality craftsmanship and the confidence of a vehicle prepared for the road ahead.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it has honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or those long-awaited weekend getaways! I've taken really good care of it, so it's all set for its next big adventure. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3 powered by the S54B32 high-pressure 3.2L inline-six. This unit features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a precise 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-Variable differential. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to prevent common floor fatigue. The VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rod bearings have been serviced to factory specifications. This example retains its factory-tuned suspension geometry, offering the tactile feedback and lateral stability expected of the chassis. While showing the honest patina of a well-driven enthusiast car, its mechanical synchronization and powertrain response remain sharp.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
